    <item>
      <title>Blain’s Farm &amp; Fleet Improves Customer Experience and Sales with Roadie Same-Day Delivery</title>
      <link>https://www.roadie.com/press-releases/blains-farm-fleet-improves-customer-experience-and-sales-with-roadie-same-day-delivery</link>
      <description>&lt;div class="hs-featured-image-wrapper"&gt; 
 &lt;a href="https://www.roadie.com/press-releases/blains-farm-fleet-improves-customer-experience-and-sales-with-roadie-same-day-delivery" title="" class="hs-featured-image-link"&gt; &lt;img src="https://46302491.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na1.net/hubfs/46302491/Imported_Blog_Media/Blains-FF-Release-Assets_01-1-1-1.jpg" alt="Blain’s Farm &amp;amp; Fleet Improves Customer Experience and Sales with Roadie Same-Day Delivery" class="hs-featured-image" style="width:auto !important; max-width:50%; float:left; margin:0 15px 15px 0;"&gt; &lt;/a&gt; 
&lt;/div&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;  &lt;/p&gt; 
