&lt;/div&gt; 
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;  &lt;strong&gt;&lt;i&gt;New solution combines UPS’s efficiency and assets with Roadie’s speed and flexibility, &lt;/i&gt;&lt;i&gt;offering retailers “bigger, faster, better” delivery&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
