      <title>Roadie Survey Finds 80% of Companies Increase Revenue With Same-Day Delivery | Roadie</title>
      <link>https://www.roadie.com/press-releases/roadie-survey-finds-80-of-companies-increase-revenue-with-same-day-delivery</link>
      <description>&lt;div class="hs-featured-image-wrapper"&gt; 
 &lt;a href="https://www.roadie.com/press-releases/roadie-survey-finds-80-of-companies-increase-revenue-with-same-day-delivery" title="" class="hs-featured-image-link"&gt; &lt;img src="https://46302491.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na1.net/hubfs/46302491/Imported_Blog_Media/ROI_of_SDD_Press_Release_Blog_Header.png" alt="Roadie Survey Finds 80% of Companies Increase Revenue With Same-Day Delivery | Roadie" class="hs-featured-image" style="width:auto !important; max-width:50%; float:left; margin:0 15px 15px 0;"&gt; &lt;/a&gt; 
&lt;/div&gt; 
&lt;h5&gt;  &lt;/h5&gt; 
&lt;h5 style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Top benefits were higher customer satisfaction, sales, and retention rates.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/h5&gt; 
